{"tid":2462590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日妻網上徵50男拍成人片　夫操刀拍攝年賺135萬被捕︰想過富裕生活","createTime":"2021-03-26T05:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T06:30:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":40,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"d8267c0d07f3ac5927ea3c0a6bd5c457b421bdc8","tid":2462590,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"日本一對30多歲的夫妻為賺錢摒棄道德，透過拍攝成人片賺大錢，由丈夫負責拍攝後製一腳踢，妻子卻當上女主角，並上網召募超過50位男性參與拍攝，至今製作了26條違法影片，一年勁賺逾1,900萬日圓（約港幣135萬）。兩夫妻上月雙雙被捕，作供時表示，犯案是為了過富裕生活。<br />\n<br />\n綜合日本傳媒報道，來自日本埼玉縣的38歲男子加藤高教，去年3月開始便與39歲妻子加藤美惠達成共識，容許妻子與其他男性發生關係，但必須讓他在旁拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n應徵條件︰35歲以下肌肉男<br />\n其後加藤美惠開始透過twitter公開召募「素人男優」，列出條件包括35歲以下、居住關東、星期六日休假、肌肉男、接受性病檢查及容許她的丈夫在旁拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n雖然沒有演出費，甚至要支付部分酒店房間費，但仍吸引大量男士應徵，至今已召募了逾50名男優參與。拍攝地點多在東京歌舞伎町的旅館，每月最少拍攝4次。<br />\n<br />\n丈夫拍攝剪接一腳踢<br />\n丈夫加藤高教拍攝剪接一腳踢，並將影片放到網絡上販賣，至今製作了26條影片，每條影片由350日圓至2,000日圓（約25至142港元）不等，共賺取逾1,900萬日圓（約港幣135萬）。加藤美惠更不時在twitter讚揚丈夫拍攝技術了得。<br />\n<br />\n至去年10月，警方在twitter發現有人徵求男優拍片，經追查下，於上月拘捕加藤高教和加藤美惠兩夫妻，並從兩人家中搜獲多部電腦、4K高清攝錄機及燈光器材。<br />\n<br />\n兩人被捕後承認罪行，加藤高教表示只為了過上富裕生活，並滿足性癖好。兩人原本只是普通打工仔，自拍成人片後致富，近一年都周身名牌，加藤美惠在被捕前更接受了隆胸手術。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2915000/2917418/japan_thumb_20210326_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2915000%2F2917418%2Fjapan_thumb_20210326_S_1024.jpg&h=e8c1a5b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e9ed5ea72f7b399fdcf457427d053c53a6acdf4","tid":2462590,"uid":121580,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"太揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b314a489e295236c85d604e172cac5805928d565","tid":2462590,"uid":121580,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"夫目前犯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccd56955e2576e671f9087bdca32c33cdeeb6b9","tid":2462590,"uid":244451,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:50:33.000Z","msg":"化左妝都屌得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947832cee179cb7b3b12560e068fd4ba25c57365","tid":2462590,"uid":46943,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"點睇佢都係基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904e41130e5462a5761ae8bb1e0a5a8860051686","tid":2462590,"uid":71913,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"947832cee179cb7b3b12560e068fd4ba25c57365","tid":2462590,"uid":46943,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"點睇佢都係基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"其實係滿足丈夫性辟好"},{"pid":"9734e4437850dd7c5de771f0bdb3cb5c7e6192a9","tid":2462590,"uid":376248,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:52:52.000Z","msg":"呢單嘢本身已經係一個AV題材"},{"pid":"902ead8817a60ea7698891cdea54afba5bb1fbca","tid":2462590,"uid":65928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef0406c4ab039932cdea9cd972dc1802b6d3073","tid":2462590,"uid":152598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"點解係犯法？"},{"pid":"04a3d3215f3741ed5bd06ee2f070ef1186f717c1","tid":2462590,"uid":137999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"無片......"},{"pid":"05d75bb9cb02d775764c13bf805b6f1e40a23625","tid":2462590